LOVE PRESENTATION
Love is good and Love is bad
Love is happy sometimes sad
Love is nothing Love is all
but into Love we always fall
Love is tainted, but mostly pure
even thoug it's insecure
Love can break your heart in two
Love can make your dreams come true
Love is kissing with sweet embraces
touching all those erotic places
Love is sweet and Love is kind
even though for some is blind
Love is good and Love is bad
Love is happy sometimes sad
Love is nothing Love is all,
yet Love seems can conquer all!

